<br>
I am 35 years old<br>
<br>
I am applying for my lvl 58 Beastlord who has 4AA's.  I dont have a magelo but  I have resist gear, lodi shield, phase spider carapace, etc.,.  AC is 1040 unbuffed/2850Hps/Wiz 170/ str 235.  And im one yellow from 59.<br>
<br>
I have been on Storm two weeks and I hail from Quellious. I came here simply to check out Legends and I love the uncrowded atmosphere so Im staying.<br>
<br>
In regards to internal guild conflict I would first try to <br>
settle any differences through tells with the other party, if that did not work and I didnt feel I could just drop the issue(Has yet to happen in my EQ exp) I would contact a guild officer.  Dont have much experience in this area cause I dont have much conflict.  Got enough in real life and thats why i play this game.<br>
<br>
Im looking to make friends, meet some hot druid chicks(preferably wood elves), and learn more about the game in terms of raiding.<br>
<br>
I play Sunday-Wednesday 9pm(EST) until 11:30 or so.<br>
Thursday and one or two Weekend nights a lot later.  <br>
<br>
I have read your guild Intro/ the DKP rules/ and the section joining L12.<br>
<br>
I dont have my epic finished(im about 1/2 way and its not really an issue with me)<br>
<br>
The only keys  I have are Sebilis.<br>
<br>
Im not an experienced raider, im willing to learn, Im and ex-Marine Officer and I take orders well(ask my wife) and dont take things personally.  I also have a lvl 60 monk with 17aa's,epic who If Im accepted I will bring from home server(hes retired now except for rare occasions).<br>
<br>
Thank you for your time and consideration.<br>
Skkoaal <br>
czimmerman000@fuse.net<br>
